# ==========================================================================
# Learn Machine Learn — environment variables
# ==========================================================================
# Copy this file to `.env.local` for local development:
#     cp .env.example .env.local
#
# `.env.local` is gitignored (see *.local in .gitignore) so your secrets
# stay out of version control. NEVER commit real tokens.
# ==========================================================================

# ------ Hugging Face Inference Provider token ------
# Used by the ML Mentor chatbot (src/components/Chatbot.jsx)
# to call https://router.huggingface.co/v1/chat/completions.
#
# Get a token:
#   1. Create an account at https://huggingface.co
#   2. Visit https://huggingface.co/settings/tokens
#   3. Create a new "Read" or "Write" token
#   4. Paste it here as VITE_HF_TOKEN below
#
# Prefixed with VITE_ so Vite exposes it to the browser at build time.
# ⚠️  Because this is exposed client-side, only use a token with the
#     minimum required scopes.
VITE_HF_TOKEN=
